import Header from '../components/Header/Header'

import StreetsterDescrip from '../components/StreetsterDescrip/StreetsterDescrip'

import logo from '../assets/logo.svg'
function Nathan() {
    return (

            <NathanContent />
            <Category />
            <StreetsterDescrip />
            <Footer />
        </section>

}

export default Nathan
